 `reachability-metadata.json` and test-only metadata to confirm the requested metadata exists.\\n./skills/review-library-update-request/SKILL.md:130:- For legacy metadata files: say metadata must use `reachability-metadata.json` and ask for old config files to be replaced.\\n./tests/tck-build-logic/src/main/java/org/graalvm/internal/tck/MetadataFilesCheckerTask.java:36: * {@code allowed-packages}, and no test-only types (§FS-repository-functional-spec.5.1).\\n./tests/tck-build-logic/src/main/java/org/graalvm/internal/tck/MetadataFilesCheckerTask.java:40:    private static final String REACHABILITY_METADATA_FILE_NAME = \\\"reachability-metadata.json\\\";\\n./tests/tck-build-logic/src/main/java/org/graalvm/internal/tck/MetadataFilesCheckerTask.java:41:    private static final String REACHABILITY_METADATA_SCHEMA_PATH = \\\"metadata/schemas/reachability-metadata-schema-v1.2.0.json\\\";\\n./tests/tck-build-logic/src/main/java/org/graalvm/internal/tck/MetadataFilesCheckerTask.java:450:        Object allowedPackagesValue = match.get(\\\"allowed-packages\\\");\\n./tests/tck-build-logic/src/main/java/org/graalvm/internal/tck/MetadataFilesCheckerTask.java:455:                \\\"Missing or invalid allowed-packages for \\\" + groupId + \\\":\\\" + artifactId +\\n./tests/tck-build-logic/src/test/java/org/graalvm/internal/tck/FixTestNativeImageRunTests.java:140:                    \\\"allowed-packages\\\" : [\\n./tests/tck-build-logic/src/test/java/org/graalvm/internal/tck/FixTestNativeImageRunTests.java:189:                      printf '{\\\"reflection\\\":[]}\\\\\\\\n' > \\\"$2/reachability-metadata.json\\\"\\n./tests/tck-build-logic/src/test/java/org/graalvm/internal/tck/FixTestNativeImageRunTests.java:202:                        printf '{\\\"reflection\\\":[]}\\\\\\\\n' > \\\"$out/reachability-metadata.json\\\"\\n./tests/tck-build-logic/src/test/java/org/graalvm/internal/tck/FixTestNativeImageRunTests.java:236:        return metadataDirectory(version).resolve(\\\"reachabilit