k-25.0.3+9.1`\\n`JAVA_HOME=/home/vjovanov/gdrive/bin/graalvm-jdk-25.0.3+9.1`\\nwith `PATH` prefixed by that `bin/`, and `native-image --version` matched Oracle GraalVM `25.0.3+9.1`. Both commands passed:\\n`./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=com.oracle.oci.sdk:oci-java-sdk-addons-sasl:3.63.1 --stacktrace`\\n`./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=com.fasterxml.jackson.core:jackson-databind:2.17.1 --stacktrace`\\n\\nThere are still unrelated workspace changes not made by this fix: `tests/src/com.oracle.oci.sdk/oci-java-sdk-addons-sasl/3.63.1/user-code-filter.json` was already modified, and Jackson native test result XMLs were regenerated by verification.\"}}\nhuman-intervention-logs/com.oracle.oci.sdk:oci-java-sdk-addons-sasl:3.63.1/metadata-fix/codex.log:291:{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_115\",\"type\":\"todo_list\",\"items\":[{\"text\":\"Verify the required GraalVM distribution/version is active for all commands\",\"completed\":true},{\"text\":\"Reproduce the OCI and Jackson test behavior under the pinned GraalVM\",\"completed\":true},{\"text\":\"Adjust metadata to satisfy both libraries without regressing existing coverage\",\"completed\":true},{\"text\":\"Run targeted verification for OCI and Jackson under the pinned GraalVM\",\"completed\":true}]}}\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
